# elite-agent crontab example
#
# Runs the poll/process/reply cycle every 5 minutes, and prints a digest of
# pending drafts once a day at 07:00. Copy the lines you want into
# `crontab -e`, then edit the path and --env/--profile flags for your
# deployment.
#
# Poll every 5 minutes:
# */5 * * * * cd /path/to/elite_agent && python3 -m elite_agent run --env .env >> /var/log/elite_agent/run.log 2>&1
#
# Daily digest of pending drafts at 07:00:
# 0 7 * * * cd /path/to/elite_agent && python3 -m elite_agent digest --env .env >> /var/log/elite_agent/digest.log 2>&1
